aboutMeContent: Hi! I'm Flor, a photographer and art director. I am passionate about creating brand identities and supporting visual creativity processes. My work is influenced by narratives and aesthetic philosophies. I aim to convey sensations, tell stories, and create distinguishable styles. I specialize in editorial photography, product photography, and working in the art department for still photography and audiovisual projects.
aboutMeContactCTA: Contact me to learn more about my services!
